CHARACTERIZE RHEOLOGY OF TWO GRADES OF POLYAMIDE AND LIQUID CRYSTAL POLYMER, AND FIT MATERIAL CONSTITUTIVE MODELS TO THE CHARACTERIZATION DATA (SECTION 3.1);
